title: Dia 4 looks for duoq [GER/ENG]

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
I wanna play to improve and climb. Please do only contact me if you are not a rager or flamer and have at least a Dia 4 MMR. I am 18 years old and mature enough to play competitively with only focusing on the beauty of the game. When playing ranked I always tryhard without making any exceptions. I am looking for someone who is able to carry while improving and someone who wants to have a great duoq experience.

My main role: mid
Do I have TS3/Skype: yes
Languages: German, English

Add me ingame if you are interested: TRK

Regards, Tom
